# #Bmob混淆

-ignorewarnings

-keepattributes SourceFile,LineNumberTable
-keepattributes Signature,*Annotation*


# keep BmobSDK
-dontwarn cn.bmob.v3.**
-keep class cn.bmob.v3.** {*;}

